<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Chicken Note</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="edn24">  24  Telescope, memorial, sword (Excalibur) and penis are conflated. The Wonderworker, a prospectus for which Leopold Bloom (in <cite>Ulysses</cite>) keeps in a drawer, was, we remember, the world's &lsquo;greatest remedy for rectal complaints direct from Wonderworker, Coventry House, South Place, London E.C.&rsquo; It appears here as, inter alia, HCE&apos;s phallus. I have also come upon appreciation in the local newspaper here in Ballydehob: </p><p class="set">O Glorious Wonderworker of Padua, Saint Anthony, Father of the poor and consoler of the afflicted, who has so thoughtfully come to my aid and consoled me so much: behold me at thy feet desiring to offer thee my sincerest gratitude.  </div>
